title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - At top, in an Oct. 21, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy hits his seventh 2015 postseason home run, during the eighth inning of Game 4 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs in Chicago. Below, Mets' Daniel Murphy celebrates after hitting the two-run home run during the eighth inning of Game 4 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs in Chicago. (AP Photo/File)
